headline: NantBioRenewables Named Finalist for Product Innovation at 2025 Reuters Global Sustainability Awards
summary: GADSDEN, Ala., August 12, 2025--NantBioRenewables is thrilled to announce that our innovative BioCal™ carbon-negative compostable straws—made with Ocean Calcium Sand and part of our Wave Ware™ brand, have been named a finalist for the prestigious Product Innovation Award at the 2025 Reuters Global Sustainability Awards. This honor reflects our commitment to pioneering sustainable business models and accelerating the transition toward a net-zero future.
